{
  "total_duration": 866.833,
  "lines": [
    {
      "i": 0,
      "start": 0.0,
      "end": 10.28,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "hook",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "今天这课先不要想成牙科恐怖故事。它其实是一个很尴尬的误会笑话：牙医一直在聊天，病人却完全说不了话。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 1,
      "start": 10.63,
      "end": 21.838,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "hook",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "想象你刚刚拔完牙，嘴里塞着"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "cotton wool"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "，药棉。你很想说一句重要的话，可是一开口只能发出含糊的声音。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 2,
      "start": 22.188,
      "end": 31.164,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "hook",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "这个时候，牙医偏偏很热情，开始问问题。"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "Dentists always ask questions when it is impossible for you to answer."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 3,
      "start": 31.513,
      "end": 45.433,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "hook",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "在中国，很多孩子想到看牙，会先想到医院口腔科。课文里的"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "dentist"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "更像预约制牙科诊所里的牙医，甚至知道病人的收藏、哥哥和新工作。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 4,
      "start": 45.783,
      "end": 52.743,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "hook",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "所以他的提问像熟人闲聊，不是坏心眼。真正好笑的是：聊天的时机完全错了。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 5,
      "start": 53.093,
      "end": 59.837,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "hook",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "他刚刚"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "pulled out one of my teeth"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "，让我"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "rest for a while"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 6,
      "start": 60.187,
      "end": 65.722,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "hook",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "我想说点什么，但是"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "my mouth was full of cotton wool"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 7,
      "start": 66.072,
      "end": 77.896,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "hook",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "他又问我的"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "match boxes"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "收藏是不是越来越多。这里中文资料里有个字看起来像误写，我们按英文理解成火柴盒。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 8,
      "start": 78.246,
      "end": 91.99,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "hook",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "Match boxes"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "是装火柴的小盒子。以前有人会收集不同地方、不同图案的火柴盒，就像今天有孩子收集贴纸、卡牌、徽章、小卡或者游戏周边。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 9,
      "start": 92.34,
      "end": 96.86,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "hook",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "然后牙医又问我哥哥怎么样，问我喜不喜欢伦敦的新工作。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 10,
      "start": 97.21,
      "end": 103.986,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "hook",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "我只能"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "either nodded or made strange noises"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "，不是点头，就是发出奇怪声音。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 11,
      "start": 104.335,
      "end": 111.527,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "hook",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "可是另一条线同时发生了："
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "Meanwhile"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "，我的舌头在找刚拔牙留下的洞。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 12,
      "start": 111.877,
      "end": 120.917,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "hook",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "外面是牙医闲聊，里面是病人警报。最后药棉拿出来，我终于能说话了：他拔错牙了。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 13,
      "start": 121.267,
      "end": 129.787,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "hook",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "现实中，牙医应该在治疗前确认牙位。课文最后一句是老课文里的夸张笑点，不是医学建议。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 14,
      "start": 130.137,
      "end": 141.817,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "hook",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "今天背诵先记中文电影线：拔牙后嘴里塞药棉、牙医闲聊、病人只能点头、舌头发现不对、最后说拔错牙。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 15,
      "start": 142.167,
      "end": 144.327,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "retell",
      "scene_meta": {
        "frame": "1"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "第一段，无法回答。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 16,
      "start": 144.677,
      "end": 149.397,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "retell",
      "scene_meta": {
        "frame": "1"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "中文锚点是：牙医总是在病人无法回答时问问题。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 17,
      "start": 149.747,
      "end": 154.266,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "retell",
      "scene_meta": {
        "frame": "1"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "先挂住开头句："
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "Dentists always ask questions"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 18,
      "start": 154.616,
      "end": 159.968,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "retell",
      "scene_meta": {
        "frame": "1"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "后面接原因场景："
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "when it is impossible for you to answer"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 19,
      "start": 160.318,
      "end": 167.958,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "retell",
      "scene_meta": {
        "frame": "1"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "这句话不是认真统计所有牙医，而是在吐槽：偏偏在最不能说话的时候，他开始问问题。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 20,
      "start": 168.308,
      "end": 173.572,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "retell",
      "scene_meta": {
        "frame": "1"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "接着进入具体故事："
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "My dentist had just pulled out one of my teeth"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 21,
      "start": 173.922,
      "end": 179.21,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "retell",
      "scene_meta": {
        "frame": "1"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "Had just pulled out"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "说明动作刚刚完成。牙已经拔完了。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 22,
      "start": 179.56,
      "end": 184.359,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "retell",
      "scene_meta": {
        "frame": "1"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "牙医还告诉我："
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "to rest for a while"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "，休息一会儿。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 23,
      "start": 184.709,
      "end": 191.869,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "retell",
      "scene_meta": {
        "frame": "1"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "这一段中文电影线是：牙医总问问题 -> 刚拔完牙 -> 让我休息 -> 可我有话要说。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 24,
      "start": 192.219,
      "end": 195.219,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "retell",
      "scene_meta": {
        "frame": "2"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "第二段，嘴里塞满药棉。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 25,
      "start": 195.569,
      "end": 201.529,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "retell",
      "scene_meta": {
        "frame": "2"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "中文锚点是：我想说话，但嘴里全是药棉，所以根本说不清。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 26,
      "start": 201.879,
      "end": 207.447,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "retell",
      "scene_meta": {
        "frame": "2"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "先看动作："
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "I tried to say something"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "。我努力想说点什么。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 27,
      "start": 207.797,
      "end": 212.037,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "retell",
      "scene_meta": {
        "frame": "2"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "但是转折来了："
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "but my mouth was full of cotton wool"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 28,
      "start": 212.386,
      "end": 220.674,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "retell",
      "scene_meta": {
        "frame": "2"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "Cotton wool"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "就是软软的药棉。拔牙后嘴里塞着药棉，正常说话会变得很困难。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 29,
      "start": 221.024,
      "end": 225.344,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "retell",
      "scene_meta": {
        "frame": "2"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "所以病人不是不礼貌，也不是不想回答。他是真的说不了话。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 30,
      "start": 225.694,
      "end": 230.214,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "retell",
      "scene_meta": {
        "frame": "2"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "这一段要读出无奈感：想说，却说不出来。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 31,
      "start": 230.564,
      "end": 233.084,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "retell",
      "scene_meta": {
        "frame": "3"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "第三段，牙医开始闲聊。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 32,
      "start": 233.434,
      "end": 242.674,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "retell",
      "scene_meta": {
        "frame": "3"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "中文锚点是：牙医知道我的火柴盒收藏，又问我的哥哥和伦敦新工作；我只能点头或发怪声。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 33,
      "start": 243.024,
      "end": 246.968,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "retell",
      "scene_meta": {
        "frame": "3"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "先看收藏："
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "He knew I collected match boxes"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 34,
      "start": 247.318,
      "end": 259.973,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "retell",
      "scene_meta": {
        "frame": "3"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "Collected"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "是“收集”。"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "Match boxes"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "是旧生活里的小收藏物，可以想成今天的贴纸、卡牌、小卡或游戏周边。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 35,
      "start": 260.323,
      "end": 264.403,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "retell",
      "scene_meta": {
        "frame": "3"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "牙医问的是："
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "whether my collection was growing"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 36,
      "start": 264.753,
      "end": 272.013,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "retell",
      "scene_meta": {
        "frame": "3"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "这里"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "whether"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "引出间接问题，不是直接说"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "Is your collection growing?"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 37,
      "start": 272.363,
      "end": 275.506,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "retell",
      "scene_meta": {
        "frame": "3"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "他又问："
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "how my brother was"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 38,
      "start": 275.856,
      "end": 279.748,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "retell",
      "scene_meta": {
        "frame": "3"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "还问："
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "whether I liked my new job in London"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 39,
      "start": 280.098,
      "end": 286.538,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "retell",
      "scene_meta": {
        "frame": "3"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "这些问题平时都很普通，像熟人关心近况。可是现在时机完全不对。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 40,
      "start": 286.888,
      "end": 292.14,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "retell",
      "scene_meta": {
        "frame": "3"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "我的回答只剩两种："
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "I either nodded or made strange noises"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 41,
      "start": 292.49,
      "end": 299.138,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "retell",
      "scene_meta": {
        "frame": "3"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "Either...or..."
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "表示二选一：要么点头，要么发出奇怪声音。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 42,
      "start": 299.488,
      "end": 301.768,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "retell",
      "scene_meta": {
        "frame": "4"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "第四段，内心警报。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 43,
      "start": 302.117,
      "end": 309.997,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "retell",
      "scene_meta": {
        "frame": "4"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "中文锚点是：与此同时，舌头在找牙洞；我突然发现不对，却说不出来；最后才说拔错牙。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 44,
      "start": 310.347,
      "end": 313.699,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "retell",
      "scene_meta": {
        "frame": "4"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "关键转场词是："
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "Meanwhile"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 45,
      "start": 314.049,
      "end": 320.721,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "retell",
      "scene_meta": {
        "frame": "4"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "Meanwhile"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "的意思是“与此同时”。它把两个画面并排放在一起。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 46,
      "start": 321.071,
      "end": 329.151,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "retell",
      "scene_meta": {
        "frame": "4"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "外线是牙医在闲聊，内线是病人的舌头在检查："
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "my tongue was busy searching out the hole"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 47,
      "start": 329.501,
      "end": 338.428,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "retell",
      "scene_meta": {
        "frame": "4"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "Searching out"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "是仔细找出来。"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "The hole where the tooth had been"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "是那颗牙原来在的位置。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 48,
      "start": 338.778,
      "end": 343.442,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "retell",
      "scene_meta": {
        "frame": "4"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "然后心理变化来了："
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "I suddenly felt very worried"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 49,
      "start": 343.792,
      "end": 348.576,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "retell",
      "scene_meta": {
        "frame": "4"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "但问题仍然没有解决："
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "but could not say anything"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 50,
      "start": 348.926,
      "end": 354.926,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "retell",
      "scene_meta": {
        "frame": "4"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "最后牙医终于把药棉拿出来："
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "removed the cotton wool from my mouth"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 51,
      "start": 355.276,
      "end": 359.54,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "retell",
      "scene_meta": {
        "frame": "4"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "我终于能告诉他："
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "he had pulled out the wrong tooth"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 52,
      "start": 359.89,
      "end": 367.725,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "retell",
      "scene_meta": {
        "frame": "4"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "这里"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "had pulled out"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "说明错误已经发生了，所以最后一句才突然有冲击力。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 53,
      "start": 368.075,
      "end": 373.487,
      "speaker": "B",
      "scene": "discuss",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "老师，这课听起来会不会很吓人？拔错牙好像很严重。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 54,
      "start": 373.837,
      "end": 383.517,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "discuss",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "现实里当然很严重，所以我们要先说清楚：真正的牙科治疗应该提前确认牙位。这篇课文把它写成夸张笑点。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 55,
      "start": 383.867,
      "end": 387.981,
      "speaker": "B",
      "scene": "discuss",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "所以不是学医学流程，是学这个误会怎么发生。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 56,
      "start": 388.331,
      "end": 394.371,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "discuss",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "对。笑点不是牙医坏，而是牙医在最不适合聊天的时候一直聊天。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 57,
      "start": 394.721,
      "end": 397.965,
      "speaker": "B",
      "scene": "discuss",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "他为什么知道病人的收藏和哥哥？"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 58,
      "start": 398.315,
      "end": 409.699,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "discuss",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "课文里的"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "dentist"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "更像牙科诊所里的熟人式牙医。他知道病人"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "collected match boxes"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "，也知道他的家庭和工作。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 59,
      "start": 410.049,
      "end": 414.798,
      "speaker": "B",
      "scene": "discuss",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "那"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "match boxes"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "是火柴盒收藏？"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 60,
      "start": 415.147,
      "end": 425.907,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "discuss",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "对。以前火柴盒很常见，不同地方的盒子可能有不同图案。今天可以联想到收集贴纸、卡牌、徽章、小卡或者游戏道具。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 61,
      "start": 426.257,
      "end": 429.58,
      "speaker": "B",
      "scene": "discuss",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "牙医问的问题在语法上有什么重点？"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 62,
      "start": 429.93,
      "end": 438.994,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "discuss",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "重点是间接问题。他没有直接原样问出来，叙述者转述成："
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "asked me whether my collection was growing"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 63,
      "start": 439.344,
      "end": 442.643,
      "speaker": "B",
      "scene": "discuss",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "还有"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "asked me how my brother was"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 64,
      "start": 442.993,
      "end": 447.185,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "discuss",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "对，还有："
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "whether I liked my new job in London"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 65,
      "start": 447.535,
      "end": 452.111,
      "speaker": "B",
      "scene": "discuss",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "这些都像闲聊，可病人嘴里有"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "cotton wool"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 66,
      "start": 452.461,
      "end": 458.117,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "discuss",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "正是这个错位。病人只能"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "either nodded or made strange noises"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 67,
      "start": 458.467,
      "end": 461.809,
      "speaker": "B",
      "scene": "discuss",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "Meanwhile"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "是另一条线？"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 68,
      "start": 462.159,
      "end": 470.571,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "discuss",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "很好。"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "Meanwhile"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "把外线和内线连起来。外线是牙医问问题，内线是舌头在找牙洞。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 69,
      "start": 470.92,
      "end": 477.465,
      "speaker": "B",
      "scene": "discuss",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "最后"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "he had pulled out the wrong tooth"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "为什么用"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "had pulled out"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "？"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 70,
      "start": 477.815,
      "end": 485.695,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "discuss",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "因为病人能说话的时候，错误已经发生了。过去完成时让最后一句变成“糟了，事情已经做完了”的 punchline。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 71,
      "start": 486.045,
      "end": 490.773,
      "speaker": "B",
      "scene": "passage_normal",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "Dentists always ask questions when it is impossible for you to answer."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 72,
      "start": 491.122,
      "end": 496.018,
      "speaker": "B",
      "scene": "passage_normal",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "My dentist had just pulled out one of my teeth and had told me to rest for a while."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 73,
      "start": 496.368,
      "end": 500.376,
      "speaker": "B",
      "scene": "passage_normal",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "I tried to say something, but my mouth was full of cotton wool."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 74,
      "start": 500.726,
      "end": 505.526,
      "speaker": "B",
      "scene": "passage_normal",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "He knew I collected match boxes and asked me whether my collection was growing."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 75,
      "start": 505.876,
      "end": 510.58,
      "speaker": "B",
      "scene": "passage_normal",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "He then asked me how my brother was and whether I liked my new job in London."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 76,
      "start": 510.93,
      "end": 515.25,
      "speaker": "B",
      "scene": "passage_normal",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "In answer to these questions I either nodded or made strange noises."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 77,
      "start": 515.6,
      "end": 520.136,
      "speaker": "B",
      "scene": "passage_normal",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "Meanwhile, my tongue was busy searching out the hole where the tooth had been."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 78,
      "start": 520.486,
      "end": 524.566,
      "speaker": "B",
      "scene": "passage_normal",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "I suddenly felt very worried, but could not say anything."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 79,
      "start": 524.916,
      "end": 531.516,
      "speaker": "B",
      "scene": "passage_normal",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "When the dentist at last removed the cotton wool from my mouth, I was able to tell him that he had pulled out the wrong tooth."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 80,
      "start": 531.865,
      "end": 534.913,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "vocab",
      "scene_meta": {
        "word": "cotton_wool"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "第一个词组："
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "cotton wool"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 81,
      "start": 535.263,
      "end": 537.159,
      "speaker": "B",
      "scene": "vocab",
      "scene_meta": {
        "word": "cotton_wool"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "cotton wool"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 82,
      "start": 537.509,
      "end": 543.653,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "vocab",
      "scene_meta": {
        "word": "cotton_wool"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "Cotton wool means soft cotton material"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "，这里就是拔牙后放在嘴里的药棉。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 83,
      "start": 544.003,
      "end": 548.099,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "vocab",
      "scene_meta": {
        "word": "cotton_wool"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "课文句子是："
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "My mouth was full of cotton wool."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 84,
      "start": 548.449,
      "end": 552.609,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "vocab",
      "scene_meta": {
        "word": "cotton_wool"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "这个词非常关键，因为它解释了为什么病人不能正常回答。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 85,
      "start": 552.959,
      "end": 560.519,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "vocab",
      "scene_meta": {
        "word": "cotton_wool"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "注意语气要轻松安全。我们不讲血腥细节，只记住：嘴里有药棉，说话不清楚。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 86,
      "start": 560.868,
      "end": 563.644,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "vocab",
      "scene_meta": {
        "word": "collection"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "第二个词："
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "collection"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 87,
      "start": 563.994,
      "end": 565.77,
      "speaker": "B",
      "scene": "vocab",
      "scene_meta": {
        "word": "collection"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "collection"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 88,
      "start": 566.12,
      "end": 571.224,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "vocab",
      "scene_meta": {
        "word": "collection"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "A collection is a group of things someone collects"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "，一组收藏品。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 89,
      "start": 571.574,
      "end": 576.222,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "vocab",
      "scene_meta": {
        "word": "collection"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "课文句子是："
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "He asked me whether my collection was growing."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 90,
      "start": 576.572,
      "end": 585.396,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "vocab",
      "scene_meta": {
        "word": "collection"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "这里的收藏是"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "match boxes"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "，火柴盒。以前有些火柴盒有不同图案，所以有人会收集。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 91,
      "start": 585.745,
      "end": 594.909,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "vocab",
      "scene_meta": {
        "word": "collection"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "今天可以想成："
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "a card collection"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "，"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "a sticker collection"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "，或者"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "a keychain collection"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 92,
      "start": 595.259,
      "end": 599.099,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "vocab",
      "scene_meta": {
        "word": "collection"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "牙医知道这个收藏，说明他是在熟人式闲聊。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 93,
      "start": 599.449,
      "end": 602.441,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "vocab",
      "scene_meta": {
        "word": "meanwhile"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "第三个词："
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "meanwhile"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 94,
      "start": 602.791,
      "end": 604.495,
      "speaker": "B",
      "scene": "vocab",
      "scene_meta": {
        "word": "meanwhile"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "meanwhile"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 95,
      "start": 604.844,
      "end": 608.78,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "vocab",
      "scene_meta": {
        "word": "meanwhile"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "Meanwhile means at the same time"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "，与此同时。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 96,
      "start": 609.13,
      "end": 614.426,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "vocab",
      "scene_meta": {
        "word": "meanwhile"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "课文句子是："
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "Meanwhile, my tongue was busy searching out the hole."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 97,
      "start": 614.776,
      "end": 621.536,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "vocab",
      "scene_meta": {
        "word": "meanwhile"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "这个词把故事切成两条线：外面牙医继续问问题，里面病人越来越紧张。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 98,
      "start": 621.886,
      "end": 628.658,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "vocab",
      "scene_meta": {
        "word": "meanwhile"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "读"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "Meanwhile"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "后面可以稍微停一下，让听的人感觉画面切换了。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 99,
      "start": 629.008,
      "end": 635.231,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "grammar",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "今天的"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "grammar board"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "叫：外线闲聊，内线警报。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 100,
      "start": 635.581,
      "end": 648.221,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "grammar",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "先看中文电影线：牙医刚拔完牙 -> 病人嘴里塞药棉 -> 牙医问收藏、哥哥和工作 -> 病人只能点头或发怪声 -> 舌头找牙洞 -> 最后说拔错牙。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 101,
      "start": 648.571,
      "end": 650.651,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "grammar",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "第一块是间接问题。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 102,
      "start": 651.001,
      "end": 654.889,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "grammar",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "直接问可以是："
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "Is your collection growing?"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 103,
      "start": 655.239,
      "end": 660.663,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "grammar",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "叙述者转述时变成："
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "asked me whether my collection was growing"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 104,
      "start": 661.013,
      "end": 664.589,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "grammar",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "再看："
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "asked me how my brother was"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 105,
      "start": 664.938,
      "end": 668.67,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "grammar",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "还有："
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "whether I liked my new job in London"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 106,
      "start": 669.02,
      "end": 672.42,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "grammar",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "这些句子都在讲牙医的 friendly small talk。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 107,
      "start": 672.77,
      "end": 675.978,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "grammar",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "第二块是"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "either...or..."
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 108,
      "start": 676.328,
      "end": 679.88,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "grammar",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "I either nodded or made strange noises."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 109,
      "start": 680.23,
      "end": 685.31,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "grammar",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "意思是我只有两个选择：要么点头，要么发出奇怪声音。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 110,
      "start": 685.66,
      "end": 690.716,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "grammar",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "生活里可以说："
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "I either wrote a note or pointed to the picture."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 111,
      "start": 691.065,
      "end": 694.137,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "grammar",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "第三块是"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "Meanwhile"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 112,
      "start": 694.487,
      "end": 701.119,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "grammar",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "Meanwhile"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "不只是“然后”。它强调同一时间另一件事正在发生。"
